value: Resident, intra-African migrant and Palearctic winter visitor, all habitats especially hilly areas but only few over forest area: breeding summer visitor Morocco - Libya; resident E South Africa; resident C Mali, much of East Africa (Eritrea - W Uganda, N Tanzania), Namibia; Madagascar (willsi);Palearctic visitors mainly north of equator.
open country, esp nr cliffs, canyons, mountains;lowlands & mountains
